messages.text: Hey there, I'm the assistant of the pharmacy. Who's there ?
Who's there? It's Hugo, but goodbye. I don't want to talk to you anymore.

It's your birthday. It might work. That is infinite beer. It comes from the infinite... It's your birthday. It's my birthday. Wait, neither authorization, neither... No. It's not going to appear if you please provide one. So? Who did you pay for? Your PC is embarrassing! Your PC is really embarrassing! That's all I have to say. It's a board program. Okay, it's perfect, it works. Oh it works! I understood! It's fine, it was fine... No wait no no no, you send me the API keys otherwise I'm going to start screaming. But how come?! How come it works? But...
